headline: Cape Town to Slap Tax Hike on Airbnb Owners
summary: Cape Town plans to more than double municipal rates on homes that are rented out for short durations, including those listed on Airbnb. Bloomberg's Jennifer Zabasajja spoke to Horizons Middle East and Africa anchor Joumanna Bercetche.
